Recommends: xdg-desktop-portal-gnome
Description: GTK4 Material You Signal Messenger client for Linux
 Signal You Messenger is a native GTK4/libadwaita Signal client for Linux,
 designed with Material You (Material Design 3) aesthetics and deep GNOME
 integration.
 .
 Features include:
  * End-to-end encryption using the Signal Protocol
  * Material You theming with adaptive accent colors
  * Native GTK4/libadwaita design for GNOME integration
  * Private and group messaging
  * Media and file sharing
  * Disappearing messages
  * System notifications with quick reply
